{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/spring/blog/blog-3/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"성장 기록 블로그","author":"kilhyeonjun","siteUrl":"https://kilhyeonjun.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"kilhyeonjun/kilhyeonjun.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"jbee"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"db5ef79f-a47b-5644-8a7b-0b297c8ab1e1","excerpt":"해당 게시물은 이 강의를 보고 제작하게되었습니다. ※ MySQL 한글 설정 및 연결 1. MySQL 한글 설정 my.ini 파일에 해당위치에 추가 시스템 언어 utf-8로 변경 하기 위함 MySQL 재시작 2. 한글 설정 확인  show variables like ‘c%‘; 3. 사용자 생성 및 권한 주기 및 DB 생성 해당 쿼리 실행해서 user 생성 및 권한 주기 4. MySQL 프로젝트 연결 src/main/resources/application.properties 확장자를 src/main…","html":"<p>해당 게시물은 이 <a href=\"https://edu.goorm.io/lecture/24605/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81%EB%B6%80%ED%8A%B8-%EB%82%98%EB%A7%8C%EC%9D%98-%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\">강의</a>를 보고 제작하게되었습니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"-mysql-한글-설정-및-연결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-mysql-%ED%95%9C%EA%B8%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%EB%B0%8F-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\" mysql 한글 설정 및 연결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>※ MySQL 한글 설정 및 연결</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1-mysql-한글-설정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-mysql-%ED%95%9C%EA%B8%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"1 mysql 한글 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. MySQL 한글 설정</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"ini\"><pre class=\"language-ini\"><code class=\"language-ini\"><span class=\"token header\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">client</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">default-character-set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">utf8</span>\n\n<span class=\"token header\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">mysql</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">default-character-set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">utf8</span>\n\n<span class=\"token header\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token section-name selector\">mysqld</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">collation-server</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span> <span class=\"token value attr-value\">utf8_unicode_ci</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">init-connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">'<span class=\"token inner-value\">SET NAMES utf8</span>'</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">init_connect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">'<span class=\"token inner-value\">SET collation_connection = utf8_general_ci</span>'</span>\n<span class=\"token key attr-name\">character-set-server</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token value attr-value\">utf8</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>my.ini 파일에 해당위치에 추가</li>\n<li>시스템 언어 utf-8로 변경 하기 위함</li>\n<li>MySQL 재시작</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-한글-설정-확인\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%ED%95%9C%EA%B8%80-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95-%ED%99%95%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"2 한글 설정 확인 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 한글 설정 확인</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 477px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 86%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"img\"\n        title=\"img\"\n        src=\"/static/ae6b0eb464f6fe039474f6aec1efc85b/d743b/mysqlutf8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ae6b0eb464f6fe039474f6aec1efc85b/5a46d/mysqlutf8.png 300w,\n/static/ae6b0eb464f6fe039474f6aec1efc85b/d743b/mysqlutf8.png 477w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 477px) 100vw, 477px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>show variables like ‘c%‘;</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"3-사용자-생성-및-권한-주기-및-db-생성\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#3-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EC%9E%90-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1-%EB%B0%8F-%EA%B6%8C%ED%95%9C-%EC%A3%BC%EA%B8%B0-%EB%B0%8F-db-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"3 사용자 생성 및 권한 주기 및 db 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. 사용자 생성 및 권한 주기 및 DB 생성</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sql\"><pre class=\"language-sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\"><span class=\"token comment\">-- 유저이름@아이피주소</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">create</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">user</span> <span class=\"token string\">'kbox'</span><span class=\"token variable\">@'%'</span> identified <span class=\"token keyword\">by</span> <span class=\"token string\">'1234'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">-- ON DB이름.테이블명</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">-- TO 유저이름@아이피주소</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">GRANT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ALL</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">PRIVILEGES</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">ON</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">TO</span> <span class=\"token string\">'kbox'</span><span class=\"token variable\">@'%'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">CREATE</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">DATABASE</span> blog <span class=\"token keyword\">CHARACTER</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">SET</span> utf8 <span class=\"token keyword\">DEFAULT</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">COLLATE</span> utf8_general_ci<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> blog<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>해당 쿼리 실행해서 user 생성 및 권한 주기</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"4-mysql-프로젝트-연결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#4-mysql-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8-%EC%97%B0%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"4 mysql 프로젝트 연결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. MySQL 프로젝트 연결</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>src/main/resources/application.properties 확장자를</li>\n<li>src/main/resources/application.yml 로 변경</li>\n<li>yaml 형식이 json과 같아 편함</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">spring</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">datasource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">driver-class-name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> jdbc<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>mysql<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>//localhost<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>3306/blog<span class=\"token punctuation\">?</span>serverTimezone=Asia/Seoul\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">username</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> kbox\n    <span class=\"token key atrule\">password</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1234</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"springboot 블로그 3.MySQL 한글 설정 및 연결","date":"September 15, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/spring/blog/blog-3/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring/blog/blog-2/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"springboot 블로그 2.의존성 설정"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring/blog/blog-4/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"springboot 블로그 4.Git 세팅"}}}}}